com.zello.sdk

Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zello.sdk.Contact

  • public class Contact
extends java.lang.Object
    The Contact class acts as a representation of a contact for the user. A Contact has a type attached to it (ie. ContactType)

      • getUsersCount

        public int getUsersCount()
         Returns the number of online users under the Contact.
 
         For ContactType.USER and ContactType.GATEWAY, this value will be 0.
 For ContactType.CHANNEL and ContactType.GROUP, this value will be the number of users online in the channel or group, respectively.
        Returns:
        number of online users under the Contact for the ContactType.

      • getUsersTotal

        public int getUsersTotal()
         Returns the number of total users under the Contact.
 
         For ContactType.USER and  ContactType.GATEWAY, this value will be 0.
        Returns:
        number of total users under the Contact for the ContactType.

      • reset

        public void reset()

        Resets the Contact instance back to the default values.

        This method will only reset the values for this copied instance of the Contact.
